                      <span>0</span>
                      votes <span class="ItemCaption">Reviewed: </span>
                      <span>2005-04-13</span>
                    </div>
                    <span>In reading eBay Secrets : How to create Internet auction listings that make 30% more money while selling every item you list, I was thoroughly astounded by the mechanisms deployed in order to be successful. 
<br />
<br />It is not rocket-science - as a matter of fact I think that's where the book's success lies - keeping it simple and straightforward to realise maximum benefit by applying these strategies. Also, the fact that it's immediately applicable. 
<br />
<br />A second remark would be to now go and test these strategies in other markets on other sites. e-Bay most definitely has the upper hand due to the volumes of traffic that uses this environment daily. It would be interesting to seek the fine-tuning nuances in lesser volumed markets, by still applying these mechanisms. 
<br />
<br />Else than that, all in all an excellent read for immediate practical application which I would highly recommend.
<br />
<br />Regards,
